### Create a short URL
POST http://localhost:8080/api/urls
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://example.com/some/very/long/path"
}

### Get by short code (replace with a real code from the response above)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/urls/vhm6LY

### 404 case
GET http://localhost:8080/api/urls/nope99

### Validation failure (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/urls
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "not a url"
}

### List all
GET http://localhost:8080/api/urls